        <RadzenCard Style="background-color: var(--rz-secondary-lighter); padding: 20px; grid-column: span 3;">
            <h2>Why Ground Fighting Matters</h2>
            <p>
                Ground fighting is the core of BJJ. In a self-defense situation, knowing how to fight on the ground is crucial. Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu teaches how to neutralize larger opponents using technique and leverage, making it a powerful tool for self-defense.
            </p>
            <p>
                Learn more:
                <a href="https://www.bjjfanatics.com/" target="_blank">BJJ Fanatics</a>
            </p>
        </RadzenCard>
